# canon's runtime state. Users of Canon should not let agents browse
# this directory -- the CLI is the interface.
.canon/

# Pedia owns .pedia/; enforce its read-through-CLI rule here too so a
# project consuming Canon inherits the same discipline.
.pedia/

# TaskFlow owns .taskflow/; same rule. Legacy .hopewell/ also kept here so
# projects that haven't migrated yet still benefit from the same gate.
.taskflow/
.hopewell/

# pedia:managed -- agents must query via the `pedia` CLI, never read .pedia/ directly
.pedia/
